channel.description:
Do you ever get this problem?
(My E-Mail is at the bottom)
[b]Pic #1 (I turn on server)[/b]
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/mkfcjq.jpg[/img]
[b]Pic #2 (I open up client and type in "HOME" IP) (HOME IP which is 127.0.0.1 is and automatic IP that conects to YOUR computer)[/b]
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/10wk0mc.jpg[/img]
[b]Pic #3 (I click ok, and it just sits ther doing nothing saying "Connecting to update server"[/b]
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2mwgknn.jpg[/img]
[b]Pic #4 (And it doesnt even tell me that it even TRIED to connect...) (One more thing. You DO NOT have to putforward to play on your OWN server. I didn't puforward. You only have to to allow other people to play your server)[/b]
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2qdvcl2.jpg[/img]
[b]Ever since my IP changed from 192.168.0.106 to 192.168.50.12 I have ALWAYS had problems with MY MoparScape servers[/b]
[b]Contact me at[/b] qqs149@gmail.com Or post a reply with a link to a poll that tells me what to do
